::Killfest/Stratus::

Stratus nods, looking at Killfest and Speedbreaker and then getting 
some of Astroblast's cargo, not sure where to take it.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
"There was a small battle against a Maximal, and I don't have the 
flight capability to get back to my base," Killfest replies, "So I 
thought I might as well speak to Motormaster while I'm here."




--- In nbwrpg@y..., Jeremiah <rdahl@s...> wrote:
> OOC: This is rAuq, I'm posting from Jer's house
> 
> ::Astroblast::
> Astroblast lands at the base. Motormaster is just off in the 
distance.
> "Speedbreaker help Stratus, a new bot, to clear my cargo bay of the 
debri
> Motormaster wanted up to take to base." Astroblast notices Killfest 
for the
> first time, "Greetings, Killfest," he says with surprise, "Why are 
you
> here? If you are looking for Motormaster he should arrive in a few
> moments." Astroblast opens his hatch and awaits the unloading.
